  "Description": "This component is a surface-mount, push-push type MicroSD (TransFlash) card connector. Its primary functionality is to provide a mechanical interface and electrical connection for a removable MicroSD memory card, facilitating data transfer and storage expansion in portable electronic devices. The connector features a card detection switch and a write-protect detection switch to interface with a host controller.",
